# Practice evidence

## Structure per study

- `RESULTS.md` — verdict PASS/FAIL/SKIPPED per step
- `artifacts/*.json` — raw API/CLI output
- `terminal*.md` — operator command log (paste-friendly)

## Citation format (PR/issues)

```text
Practice evidence Study NN — docs/governance/practice-evidence/study-NN-*/RESULTS.md
Artifact: study-NN-*/artifacts/<file>.json
```

## Cross-study index

Update `PRACTICE_STUDIES_AUDIT_01-07.md` gap registry when adding studies; do not remove documented gaps without new evidence.

## Network claims

- Study 06 = LAN `192.168.x`
- Study 07 = Tailscale `100.x` only — do not infer hotspot disconnect without log (G-03).
